==Korean==
===Adjective===
'''많다''' ('''manta''')
#[[many]], [[much]], a lot, plentiful
#:오늘 전시회 방문자가 '''많다''' (''Oneul jeonsihoe bangmunjaga manta''). Today there are many visitors at the exhibition.
#:돈이 '''많은''' 사람 (''Doni manheun saram''). Someone who has a lot of money / A rich person

